{"tid":198181,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【用良幣驅逐劣幣】一人 N 個你追緊 / 追過既高質 POST","createTime":"2017-04-12T10:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T11:56:57.000Z","uid":39120,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e375a3eb03af6f9c4541dc08467e863f9ed938a7","tid":198181,"uid":39120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"連登熱門充斥住低質罵戰、私怨、淫亂私生活上黎博出位、膠post等等，好多值得追下既高質post都反而沉得好快，無人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不如巴絲打一人講幾個你追緊/追過又覺得係 高質post / 強帖 出黎，等多D人睇到推返上黎啦（最好無上過熱門，因為熱門既應該唔少人睇過） 唔一定係新post，你睇過覺得正既都可以講下，我都想搵多D高質post 追下，<br />\n一開熱門、吹水台好多垃圾，上上下連登睇極都呢D垃圾會覺得好無癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊用良幣驅逐劣幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先歡迎定義下心目中既高質post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能個個唔同既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得高質post不限一種既，例如可以係<br />\n&mdash; 內容豐富，資訊性，睇完學到野既；<br />\n&mdash; 爭議性題目雙方據理力爭、認真討論，廣闊到雙方眼界，唔係小學雞互鬧；<br />\n&mdash; 有創意、好睇既故事；<br />\n&mdash; 娛樂性高，可以係真係好搞笑、或者好多靚既、得意既圖，睇完會開心左既；<br />\n&mdash; 歡迎再講多D<br />\n<br />\n講完咁多，拋磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望巴絲打貼埋link同簡單講下咩黎，方便大家搵啱心水既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>只要影張相，我就可以知道你既過去同未來。</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/6770/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/6770/page/1</a><br />\n近來係講故台見到開始追，但未追到LIVE，個題材好吸引到我，樓豬既文筆都幾啱我心水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>同男朋友拍拖既「潛規則」</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/105166/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/105166/page/1</a><br />\n舊post黎，唔單止樓豬講既方法值得學習，post入面都有講起情侶應該點樣化解矛盾，唔係剩係話「溝通多d」而係點樣入手去溝通，我覺得（尤其絲打）睇完應該會學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未拍拖既巴絲打都取定經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>【歐遊百幾日】歐洲exchange四圍去 東中西南歐 ( 遊記 + 你問我答 ) 2</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/188509/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/188509/page/1</a><br />\n超多靚相同巨量資訊既歐遊post，樓豬當中遇過既痴線經歷都超搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會千字文式答巴絲打問題，入面D巴絲打都有豐富歐遊經驗，幫手比到勁多有用補充資訊，準備去、去過或者無諗過去歐遊既巴絲打都啱睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我去過歐洲都追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 舊post講荷蘭，而家講緊巴爾幹半島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>[整合]關西十日之旅超展開</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/142762/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/142762/page/1</a><br />\n感覺上係上面個post既日本關西版，多資訊、好詳盡同埋又係可以瘋狂問瘋狂答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>有咩人物係畀三國演義美化得太勁</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/195582/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/195582/page/1</a><br />\n個討論幾多野睇，唔係得D人名，有人物故事睇下，作為唔係歷史JJ覺得幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>同居情侶處理分手？</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/186801/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/186801/page/1</a><br />\n呢個post正既位今次唔係樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係D回覆，就住同居呢個議題討論，有巴絲打會分享自己失敗或者成功既例子同心得，都有人失敗過學到野，我覺得當中所提到既相處方法都係值得學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人覺得精華係 #150 #200 #211，幫到唔少女人解答點解男人有少成日話攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋學下體諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>[理性討論］其實賣黃牛係咪真係好似口中咁十惡不赦？</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/178228/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/178228/page/1</a><br />\n我唔撐黃牛，都憎黃牛，但覺得post入面既討論好認真，雙方既理據都會令自己諗得廣D，唔係低質粗口罵戰/抽水恥笑/批鬥，所以覺得值得一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">突發！又有仆街棄養</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/191150/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/191150/page/1</a><br />\n樓主救左小貓一隻，但重點唔係度，係見到好多巴絲打都好有心即刻比物資佢一齊救隻貓，好有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有佢地講好多養貓心得，我無養貓但想養小動物，睇完都覺得學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">連登倉鼠奴出晒嚟！！！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/177784/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/177784/page/1</a><br />\n好多高質可愛搞笑倉鼠圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇完好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴絲打一齊開心share下追緊咩高質post!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab2f0bdbd291a4b4d22fec94878e05c4f6fb6df","tid":198181,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:45:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/87314/page/40?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/87314/page/40?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"65cdbe5afc929cf36c059d4f0aef347c8e1a1ecd","tid":198181,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:47:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"511239180c556bb82137180aecf5403658698c4b","tid":198181,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6f8eeb2f95ff2ad3e5ec2485e37c4f01abbec56","tid":198181,"uid":39120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/87314/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/87314/page/1</a></blockquote><br />\n幫巴打補返post名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n[齊齊黎睇故仔啦喂]no sleep/靈異/超自然系列<br />\n[屎忽痕] no sleep 恐怖短故翻譯"},{"pid":"32d4cfceefd7a2948f0f4ca571e48f0fd1ae555b","tid":198181,"uid":39120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>post你係街見到幾靚嘅男仔(2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/60723/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/60723/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n原來係肥絲既攝影作品集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99ba73f2894f218bb141f8643df01689dda480f","tid":198181,"uid":39120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8fc0cc43a6cbede9b0d2fdf2f8b886685dbf9d","tid":198181,"uid":39120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:00:55.000Z","msg":"發現藍色一到黑底好難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>只要影張相，我就可以知道你既過去同未來。</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/6770/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/6770/page/1</a><br />\n近來係講故台見到開始追，但未追到LIVE，個題材好吸引到我，樓豬既文筆都幾啱我心水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>同男朋友拍拖既「潛規則」</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/105166/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/105166/page/1</a><br />\n舊post黎，唔單止樓豬講既方法值得學習，post入面都有講起情侶應該點樣化解矛盾，唔係剩係話「溝通多d」而係點樣入手去溝通，我覺得（尤其絲打）睇完應該會學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未拍拖既巴絲打都取定經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>【歐遊百幾日】歐洲exchange四圍去 東中西南歐 ( 遊記 + 你問我答 ) 2</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/188509/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/188509/page/1</a><br />\n超多靚相同巨量資訊既歐遊post，樓豬當中遇過既痴線經歷都超搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會千字文式答巴絲打問題，入面D巴絲打都有豐富歐遊經驗，幫手比到勁多有用補充資訊，準備去、去過或者無諗過去歐遊既巴絲打都啱睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我去過歐洲都追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 舊post講荷蘭，而家講緊巴爾幹半島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>[整合]關西十日之旅超展開</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/142762/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/142762/page/1</a><br />\n感覺上係上面個post既日本關西版，