ld;\">連登倉鼠奴出晒嚟！！！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/177784/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/177784/page/1</a><br />\n好多高質可愛搞笑倉鼠圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇完好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2752aabba77a3eb0efa92df17b29148fa4fe1c","tid":198181,"uid":39120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:08:36.000Z","msg":"連登無高質post？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23704f2980d116378593444ba97c15c0513f9b02","tid":198181,"uid":39120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f219261807a4335f293a310a71f80606c49bbb3a","tid":198181,"uid":39120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3291eb4e21edac8eacbe4dd7c2b4ba5131274f91","tid":198181,"uid":39120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09ea22dc52ab0a45b37e4946eb9b298bfdfdb8c","tid":198181,"uid":39120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}